title: MasterChef.The.Professionals.S07E11.PDTVx264.mp4
description: The final first-round heat sees five more chefs enter the kitchen, with the first challenge giving them an hour to cook a plate of food that showcases their culinary skills, before one is asked to leave. The remaining four try to impress Monica Galetti by preparing three canapes, after which Marcus Wareing asks them to make a spectacular crab dish. The judges then decide which three have earned a place in the next round
